   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>. . . I salute your children and their mothers and your mother. Anthestias salute you, each by name. The children salute you, each by name. We salute Castrensis and Lucretius together with his children and wife. I pray for your good health.  . . . your names at the top of the papyrus roll and the documents(?).  . . .;(Verso) [To - - -] from Chairemonianos.</ab>
